name: Demo II: Amiga Public Domain Collection
overview: Volume 2 of the DEMO series contains over 600 Megabytes of software and more for your Amiga, including: Games - Over 100 PD games ready to run with a simple front end menu Animations - Watch large animations spooling from CD Sound Samples - Over 6000 IFF and raw sound samples for use in music creation programs Music Modules - Over 2000 Protracker modules with players Demos - Latest PD demos and the best of the classic demos Images - 100s of images (IFF format). And much more!
